bVIEW Instructions 

1. ### Setting Up Bluetooth Port
  <p>Open NI-VISA Configuration</p>
  <p>Using one of the Serial ports, edits it's settings</p>
  <p>Under binding, edit to be the calling unit device port for the Bluetooth device</p>
  <p>Save changes to VISA Configuration</p>

2. ### Running LabVIEW Application
  <p>Run LabVIEW application</p>
  <p>Select VISA Resource Name via the drop down menu on the user interface</p>
  </br>
  <p>Flip the Data switch to begin reading information from the hardware</p>
